Bootstrap a Sinatra application with Html5-boilerplate already include.

Usage:
- bundle install
- ruby app.rb

Use:
- Sinatra : http://www.sinatrarb.com
- Html5-boilerplate : http://html5boilerplate.com/
- Haml and Sass : http://haml-lang.com
- Partials like in Rails : https://gist.github.com/119874

There is no:
- database pre-configured
- models, controllers... Just a plain simple Sinatra app !

